      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Ready for a new chapter! This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a fantastic opportunity for someone looking for a dependable ride at a great value. While it shows some honest wear from its time on the road, it remains a functional and spirited choice for your daily commutes or weekend errands!",
