    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic ride. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, it handles beautifully and feels great on the road. It\u2019s clean, well-cared for, and ready to go! Send me a message if you'd like to come take a look\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
